casebody.data:
Sibilia’s Estate. Argued January 8, 1924. Before Frazer, Walling, Simpson, Kephart, Sadler and Schaffer, JJ. *463Benjamin L. Steinberg, for appellant,

cited: Cleveland & P. R. R. v. Rowan, 66 Pa. 393.

Wilbur F. Galbraith, for appellee,

cited: Michigan Cent. R. R. v. Vreeland, 227 U. S. 59; Taylor v. Taylor, 232 U. S. 363; St. Louis, I. M. & S. Ry. v. Craft, 237 U. S. 648.

February 14, 1924: Per Curiam,

The appeal is dismissed at appellant’s costs on the opinion of the Superior Court and it is ordered that distribution be made therein as directed.
